<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.3.9">
<l>mīṉamar poykai nāṇmalar koyvāṉ vēṭkaiyi ṉōṭuceṉ ṟiḻinta</l>
<l>kāṉamar vēḻaṅ kaiyeṭut talaṟak karāvataṉ kāliṉaik katuva</l>
<l>vāṉaiyiṉ tuyaran tīra<supplied>p</supplied>puḷ  ḷūrntu ceṉṟuniṉ ṟāḻitoṭ ṭāṉai</l>
<l>tēṉamar cōlai māṭamā mayilait tiruvallik kēṇikkaṇ ṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When a forest-dwelling elephant which stooped [at] a fish-dwelling pond,</l>
<l>Arriving with the desire to pluck fresh flowers, cried out, raising its trunk,</l>
<l>As a crocodile grabbed its leg, the one who, arriving riding a bird,</l>
<l rend="indent">used a discus to destroy the elephant’s suffering,</l>
<l>I saw at Tiruvallikkēṇi in great Māyilai with mansions and honeyed groves.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
